title: Quynh Nhi
typeOfFood: Ovo, Thai, Delivery, Take-out, Vietnamese, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Vietnamese food restaurant. The fruit shakes can be made dairy-free. The vegetarian/vegetable dishes reportedly do not contain fish or fish sauce. Separate vegetarian menu including spring rolls, tofu fresh rolls, tofu vermicelli bowl, and vegetable and tofu stir fry. Makes a variety of pad thai - ask for vegan.
